# ChangeLog for PyCertbot

This document maintains a chronologically ordered list of notable changes to the PyCertbot project.

The version format is based on release date and is structured as follows: `YYYY.MM.DD-REL`.

## [Unreleased]

- Initial planning and design phase.
- Identified client-side integration via SMTP and IMAP protocols.
- Devised a new privacy-preserving registration protocol.
- First implementation of the PyCertbot API (server)

## [2024.04.17-0]

### Added
- Initial release of PyCertbot.
- Features include:
  - Support for standard SMTP and IMAP protocols.
  - Provides a scriptable interface for automation.
  - Integration with existing email infrastructure in a non-disruptive manner.
  - Comprehensive documentation on usage and configuration.

### Changed
- N/A

### Deprecated
- N/A

### Removed
- N/A

### Fixed
- N/A

### Security
- Implemented basic security features to ensure safe use of TLS for communication.

